## Android adaptive icon requirements:

- **Foreground**: 1024x1024 PNG (icon content)
- **Background**: Solid color or simple pattern
- **Safe area**: Keep important elements in center 66% of icon
- **Mask**: System applies various shapes (circle, square, etc.)

## Suggested design:

- **Foreground**: Emergency/disaster response symbol
- **Background**: Solid color matching app theme
- **Safe area**: Icon centered in 66% area
- **Colors**: Use app's color palette

## Tools for creating adaptive icons:

- **Android Studio**: Built-in adaptive icon editor
- **Figma**: https://figma.com (with adaptive icon templates)
- **Sketch**: https://sketch.com
- **Adobe Illustrator**: https://adobe.com/illustrator

